MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Dimension transformation for D_GamingMachine. Transforms rows from DACOM table DEVICE, joining to mac_config to get the Machine Type. Since mac_config contains many rows per device_id, we must aggregate back down to one row per device_id.
MAPPING.NAME: m_GamingMachine

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: User Defined Join
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: S_DACOM_Device.manufacturer = UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.c_short AND S_DACOM_Mac_Config.mac_type = UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_T.c_short AND S_DACOM_Mac_Config.groups *= UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_B.c_short AND S_DACOM_Mac_Config.device_id = S_DACOM_Device.device_id AND S_DACOM_Mac_Config.mach_stat = 'N' and S_DACOM_Device.PtyLocNum = UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_M.PtyLocNum and S_DACOM_Device.PtyLocNum = UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_T.PtyLocNum and S_DACOM_Mac_Config.PtyLocNum *= UVW_S_DACOM_Class_Code_B.PtyLocNum and S_DACOM_Device.PtyLocNum = S_DACOM_Mac_Config.PtyLocNum and S_DACOM_Device.PtyLocNum = $$Property_no

INSTANCE.DESCRIPTION: Set the update strategy to INSERT
INSTANCE.NAME: Upd_D_GamingMachine_New

INSTANCE.DESCRIPTION: Separate New rows from updates. Discard rows that have not changed.
INSTANCE.NAME: Rtr_NewUpdate

INSTANCE.DESCRIPTION: Set the update strategy to Update
INSTANCE.NAME: Upd_D_GamingMachine_Update

INSTANCE.DESCRIPTION: Join Device to Mac_Config to get Machine Type.
INSTANCE.NAME: SQ_GetUniqueDevices

INSTANCE.DESCRIPTION: Lookup the target table, and allocate surrogate keys for new rows.
INSTANCE.NAME: DCLkp_D_GamingMachine

INSTANCE.DESCRIPTION: Derive values for the target table columns
INSTANCE.NAME: Exp_TransformTargets
